2007;;My Daughter, My Angel (Ma fille mon ange);;Canadian;;Alexis Durand-Brault;;Michel Côté, Karine Vanasse;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/My_Daughter,_My_Angel;;Germain Dagenais, a former solicitor (Côté), discovers evidence from a crime scene which included a dead body, of a videotape that included pornography. He is interested in viewing porn during his private time and accidentally finds his own daughter Nathalie (Karine Vanasse) in a video announcing she will be in a future video. Panicked, Germain must find his daughter and save her before she meets the same fate.